      • publishStop

        public void publishStop()
        Stops the publishing functionality.

        All subsequent publish are not sent over the platform until the publishStart() method is not called.

      • publishStart

        public void publishStart()
        Starts the publishing functionality if it was stopped otherwise does nothing.

        All publish made during the stop status are sent over the Platform.
